body:
Hey everyone!

Since I am very close to reaching 500 subscribers on YouTube, I have decided to make a really special video; something that I haven't done before.

Therefore, I'll be doing a video Q&A and answering every question you ask me!

Some guidelines when asking me questions:
  • You may ask a maximum of 4 or 5 questions.
  • I will answer ANY question you ask me, regardless of how immature it may be.
  • Post your questions either on this thread or on the video that I will link below.
For more information about the Q&A, you can watch this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iOGOf5l9ntA

Thanks everyone, I'm really looking forward to this!
